Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:27.36,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Pure Purepa-redo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:30.27,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}总有一天会逮到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:45.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是大意那根手指就会
